&lt;img width="1280" height="960" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d0e7d8bd-f2b0-41f5-b892-60db414b7571" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;가족들한테 밥도 샀다. 15만원이 뭐라고&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1179" height="2556" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d9a8256a-373a-41fe-9b86-4fe6dadfe470" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;먹고싶던 음료를 생각없이 사먹었는데 맛있었다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>요즘</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog40/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog40/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="요즘"&gt;
