&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9e3fb442-5b19-4ae5-9bdb-e806020b38b7" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="959" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d0d1b5c6-eef2-4297-ab5f-147cdfd74f10" /&gt;
