&lt;p&gt;엄마가 만들어준 샌드위치&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/28ad17f9-019e-44b4-9660-10c0a49f60f1" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;운동을 다시 시작했다&lt;/p&gt;
