 완전한날
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%99%84%ec%a0%84%ed%95%9c%eb%82%a0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2024-01-25&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f0c23bb1-f520-4312-a4b8-c50653c59c45" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;내가 행복하면 남들은 눈에들어오지않는다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;새로산 틴트가 마음에 들구 새로산 가디건두 맘에 든다 ㅎ 하나 더 살까 고민중.
오늘 얼굴상태도 맘에든다. 옷도 괜찮다. 공부도 맘에 든다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/febd2e92-41cb-4a3d-a20a-1d9cea3ee3a0" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;운동도 하고 집에 왔다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;집와서 블루베리랑 귤이랑 사과랑 자유시간이랑 초콜릿남은거 먹었다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>꾸려나가는일상</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog18/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog18/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="꾸려나가는일상"&gt;
 꾸려나가는일상
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ea%be%b8%eb%a0%a4%eb%82%98%ea%b0%80%eb%8a%94%ec%9d%bc%ec%83%81"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2024-01-15&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오늘은 운동도 하고 공부는 조금만했지만 괜찮고 말실수도 안했고. 엄마한테 기분좋은일도 안겨주었고 화목 7시부터 8시까지하는 요가수업도 신청했다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;식단을 지키고 엄마와 거리를 유지하면서 주변사람을 잘챙기고, 돈을 적당히 쓰고, 사람에게 화내지않고, 말을 많이 하지말고 잘 졸업하자&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1179" height="1263" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f4afcbd4-8e1f-4a41-8413-53e314bc4986" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="459" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c144cbdc-1a29-4d76-aa61-87e3219ca54c" /&gt;</description></item><item><title>오랜만에 찐한카공</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog20/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog20/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="오랜만에-찐한카공"&gt;
 오랜만에 찐한카공
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%98%a4%eb%9e%9c%eb%a7%8c%ec%97%90-%ec%b0%90%ed%95%9c%ec%b9%b4%ea%b3%b5"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2024-01-13&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ecc7fa90-2901-400a-b164-fa86de060daa" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/86963573-d3c6-4e20-861e-dd730a1f1925" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;새로생긴 투썸을 엄마랑만 와봤었는데 오늘 혼자와서 논문도 찾고 생각도하고 새로산 베이지안통계책도 읽었다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>마음</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog21/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog21/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="마음"&gt;
 마음
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%a7%88%ec%9d%8c"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2024-01-05&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bba57942-dcc5-4a5a-8951-ad1682576228" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;남들이 생각하는거에 맘쓰지말자&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;내할일들을 널브려놓고 그속에 파묻혀 할일을하자&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>생일생일</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog1/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="생일생일"&gt;
 생일생일
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%83%9d%ec%9d%bc%ec%83%9d%ec%9d%bc"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2024. 1. 1. 20:58&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/26c95ca3-9898-4800-979b-5b8f04d2ba14" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;31일에 길이랑 지수 만나서 라멘 먹으러갔다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/585b2d96-0930-4771-8aa9-71d6cad8e316" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;소품샵도 가구&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b05be3ce-2004-4a4d-9da9-645d46cb38ce" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;길혜민 추천 카페에 들어왔는데 운좋게 소파자리가 비어서 앉았다 ㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c6594cd0-7694-4aeb-99f9-e69ca074f5d8" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;같이찍은 인생네컷 헤헤 맘에들엉&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1fa0b73c-8924-4e19-bdba-865e6c45a229" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;화장실 갔는데 포스터가 예뻐서..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1179" height="2556" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/73bf9265-5b7b-4b9d-bdb7-47d8f8233a1e" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;김윤지가 내 카톡에 답장없었나 그래서 생일겸 한번더보냈는데 진짜 미안해하는게 느껴져서 아주조금이나마 서운했던게 없어지고 힘들겠다는생각도 들었당&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4338db35-6cba-4935-b745-74e67c1da4e9" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오늘(생일)은 평화로운 시간을 위해 스카에 가서 지수가 사준 다이어리를 개시했다 ㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e397ae52-afad-4899-8e8e-c7f8f95f1067" /&gt;
